@startuml
title UML state machine diagram

state "Create account" as CreateAccount
CreateAccount : entry/Allow user to create an account
CreateAccount : do/Register new user
CreateAccount : exit/Successful registration

state "Login" as Login
Login : entry/Allow user to log in
Login : do/Login using valid username and password
Login : exit/Invalid login / To home page

state "Check weather" as CheckWeather
CheckWeather : entry/Allow user to check the weather
CheckWeather : do/Show selected weather information
CheckWeather : exit/To home page

state "View additional details" as ViewDetails
ViewDetails : entry/Allow user to view additional details
ViewDetails : do/Show alerts, weekly analysis, future prediction or graph
ViewDetails : exit/To home page

state "Logout" as Logout
Logout : entry/End the session when user logs out
Logout : do/Logout user
Logout : exit/Successful logout

[*] --> CreateAccount : [check user]
CreateAccount --> Login : [new user]

Login --> [*] : [Improper]
Login --> CheckWeather : [Proper]

CheckWeather --> ViewDetails
ViewDetails --> Logout
Logout --> [*]

@enduml
